<h2 class='mt-2' style='border-bottom:1px solid #ebebeb;'>Rewards</h2>
<div style='color:#ebebeb;'>
    <h4 class='mt-4' stye='color:#ebebeb'>Add a reward</h4>
    <p class='mt-2' style='text-align:justify'>You may create a new reward from the Reward Library. The library contains many rewards in a variety of categories that provide a long list of ideas for rewards your advocated
    would be excited about. It's recommended to have rewards of different types (eg. one reward from each category) to allow your advocates to find the rewards they like the most.</p>
    <p style='text-align:justify'>Once you select a reward, you will be able to customize it (name, description, image, points required for redemption, etc).</p>
    <p style='text-align:justify'>You can select a reward from the categories below, or create one from scratch.</p>
    <button class='btn btn-primary' id='scratch' style="float:right;margin-top:20px">Create Reward From Scratch</button>
</div>